Instead of using TIC data I could use EPFR with weekly and monthly frequency, and then use quarterly BPM data following Forster et al. (2014) to see if frequency plays a role. Note also, the authors did not normalize the flows per GDP.},
author = {Sarno, Lucio and Tsiakas, Ilias and Ulloa, Barbara},
doi = {10.1016/j.jimonfin.2015.03.006},
